handist.collections.dist

Class DistChunkedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • handist.collections.ChunkedList<T>
      • handist.collections.dist.DistChunkedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of elements handled by this DistChunkedList
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    apgas.util.SerializableWithReplace, DistributedCollection<T,DistChunkedList<T>>, RangeRelocatable<LongRange>, Serializable, Iterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DistCol

    public class DistChunkedList<T>
extends ChunkedList<T>
implements DistributedCollection<T,DistChunkedList<T>>, RangeRelocatable<LongRange>, apgas.util.SerializableWithReplace
    A class for handling objects at multiple places. It is allowed to add new elements dynamically. This class provides the method for load balancing.

    Note: In the current implementation, there are some limitations.

    • There is only one load balancing method: the method flattens the number of elements of the all places.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
